(5. Independent Study Guidance) Tj
T*
(For independent study, the learner should revisit the explanation and then practise with) Tj
T*
(tasks that reflect naming and identifying organic compounds. The most effective habit is) Tj
T*
(to read the worked example slowly, restate each step in simple words, and then attempt a) Tj
T*
(similar question alone. This turns Organic Chemistry into something the student can) Tj
T*
(genuinely study and understand without depending completely on a teacher.) Tj
T*
() Tj
