T*
(as an exam topic.) Tj
T*
(- The learner must understand carbon chains, functional groups, and common reactions) Tj
T*
(because it controls how questions in Organic Chemistry are answered correctly.) Tj
T*
(- A strong answer in Organic Chemistry uses the correct chemical reasoning process and) Tj
T*
(explains why that method fits the task.) Tj
T*
