(Step-By-Step Method) Tj
T*
(1. Read the question or example and identify the part connected to Organic Chemistry.) Tj
T*
(2. Recall the specific rule, process, or principle behind carbon chains, functional) Tj
T*
(groups, and common reactions.) Tj
T*
(3. Apply the correct chemical reasoning process step by step instead of jumping to the) Tj
T*
(answer.) Tj
T*
(4. Check the result carefully and confirm that it matches the requirement of the topic.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
