T*
(that the question is testing.) Tj
T*
(3. Apply the correct method for Organic Chemistry step by step without skipping) Tj
T*
(reasoning.) Tj
T*
(4. Check the final answer and explain why it is correct.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Worked Example 2) Tj
T*
(1. Choose a second example that still focuses on naming and identifying organic) Tj
T*
(compounds.) Tj
